    "body": "R installs plenty of packages which it considers `recommended_packages`, these packages coming from this variant `--with-recommended-packages` and is default during compilation.\r\nNew variant gives you the option to do it by `--without-recommended-packages` and main motivation is, when e.g. `r-cluster` is install by Spack during activation it getting blocked owing to existence of `cluster` which installed as `recommended-packages`.",
